name: Sawun Luajaw Veagiuna (Enemy Base)
description: A big, tough level with losta monsters and lotsa nasty trix. This is pretty good layout in the level and just dont expect the same level from me as in past. Your mission is to gun down all the bad guys before they gun you down. There are 8 secrets in the level 1 secret very hard to find which contains last boss. My beast level will scare u, fun time!
